    <details class="faq-item">
      <summary>Does my child need any coding experience?</summary>
      <p class="faq-answer">Not at all. Our camps are built for kids who've never touched a robot or written a single line of code.</p>
    </details>

    <details class="faq-item">
      <summary>What if my child can't read yet?</summary>
      <p class="faq-answer">No problem. Kids program with colorful blocks and icons, not text. No reading needed.</p>
    </details>

    <details class="faq-item">
      <summary>Will my child see results quickly?</summary>
      <p class="faq-answer">Yes — small steps mean the first "IT WORKS!" moment comes fast. Success on day one.</p>
    </details>

    <details class="faq-item">
      <summary>Does my child need to handle soldering or wiring?</summary>
      <p class="faq-answer">All the hard parts — soldering, wiring, setup — are done by the engineer. Your child gets the fun: building, programming, and commanding the mission.</p>
    </details>
